alia/USA) * [[Mary McGuckian]] (Ireland/UK) * [[Danica McKellar]] (USA) * [[Nancy McKeon]] (USA) * [[Tawnia McKiernan]] (USA) * [[Carolyn McMaster]] (Canada) * [[Mr. & Mrs. Sidney Drew|Lucile McVey]] (2nd Mrs. Sidney Drew) (USA) * [[Nancy Meckler]] (UK) * [[Maria de Medeiros]] (Portugal) * [[Deepa Mehta]] (Canada/India) * [[Vijaya Mehta]] (India) * [[Hu Mei]] (China) * [[Ursula Meier]] (France) * [[Anna Melikian]] (Russia) * [[Kay Mellor]] (UK) * [[Linda Mendoza]] (USA) * [[Nina Menkes]] * [[Anjali Menon]] (India) * [[Agnès Merlet]] (France) * [[Marziyeh Meshkini]] (Iran) * [[Leah Meyerhoff]] (USA) * [[Nancy Meyers]] (USA) * [[Anne-Marie Miéville]] (Switzerland) * [[Liu Miaomiao (director)|Liu Miaomiao]] (China) * [[Vanessa Middleton]] (USA) * [[Tamineh Milani]] (Iran) * [[Elisa Miller]] * [[Rebecca Miller]] (USA) * [[Sharron Miller]] (USA) * [[Pilar Miró]] (Spain) * [[Adrienne Mitchell]] (Canada) * [[Martha Mitchell (director)|Martha Mitchell]] (USA) * [[Jill Mitwell]] (USA) * [[Ariane Mnouchkine]] (France) * [[Tracey Moffat]] (Australia) * [[Hengameh Mofid]] * [[Hillie Molenaar]] * [[Karen Moncrieff]] (USA) * [[Adriana Monti]] (Italy) * [[Christine Moore (director)|Christine Moore]] (USA) * [[Jocelyn Moorhouse]] * [[Soudabeh Moradian]] * [[Yolande Moreau]] (Belgium) * [[Jeanne Moreau]] (France) * [[Stephanie Morgenstern]] * [[Makoto Moriwaki]] (Japan) * [[Carol Morley]] (UK) * [[Judy Morris]] * [[Dee Mosbacher]] * [[Kim Moses]] (USA) * [[Emilia Mosquito]] * [[Granaz Moussavi]] (Iran) * [[Kira Muratova]] (Soviet Union) * [[Beth Murphy]] * [[Alison Murray]] (Canada/UK) * [[Jinna Mutune]] (Kenya) * [[Gloria Muzio]] (USA) {{div col end}}
