Utagawa_Toyoharu_-_A_Winter_Party_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg|alt=Painting of a three Japanese woman entertaining two Japanese men|''A Winter Party''<br/>[[Utagawa Toyoharu]], mid-18th&nbsp;– late 19th century
